# Security headers for all routes (Cloudflare Pages).
# Safe, non-breaking hardening. CSP is frame-ancestors ONLY (allows the
# Restoration AI app's Site-tab preview to embed the site) — no full CSP here
# (full CSP needs per-site tuning against the third-party stack and can break the page).
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://app.restorationai.io http://localhost:5173
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
